OL,3,C'Our mum, our loving nanna': Tribute
OL,4,Cto woman killed crossing road
OL,6,FThe family of a woman who died when
OL,7,Fshe was hit by an HGV as she was
OL,8,Fcrossing a road say they have "had
OL,9,Ftheir hearts broken".
OL,11,FBrenda Rostron, 63, from was killed in
OL,12,Fthe collision on Spotland Road on 1
OL,13,FFebruary 2024.
OL,15,FA 32-year-old man arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of causing death by careless
OL,17,Fdriving has been released under
OL,18,Finvestigation.
