OL,3,C'Our mum, our loving nanna': Tribute
OL,4,Cto woman killed crossing road
OL,6,FIn tribute to her, Brenda's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "Brenda is our mum, she is a
OL,8,Floving nanna to our children and a
OL,9,Ffriend to many.
OL,11,F"We have had our hearts broken at the
OL,12,Fnews of her passing. No one should
OL,13,Flose someone they love in this way,
OL,14,Fand all we want now is to be able to
OL,15,Fgrieve as a family in peace and
OL,16,Fremember her and all the special
OL,17,Fmemories we have of her."
