OL,3,C'Our mum, our loving nanna': Tribute
OL,4,Cto woman killed crossing road
OL,6,FThe family has also asked people to
OL,7,Fstop sharing pictures of the scene
OL,8,Fonline, saying it has caused them
OL,9,F"indescribable pain."
OL,11,FPolice Constable Philip Drummond of 's
OL,12,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit
OL,13,Fsaid: "This has come as devastating
OL,14,Fnews to Brenda's family and the images
OL,15,Fcirculating online have caused
OL,16,Fdistress and pain to a grieving family.
OL,18,F"I want to echo their words and ask
OL,19,Fthat any images or footage of this
OL,20,Fincident be taken down.
